    <section id="overview" class="tutorial-section">
        <h2>1. Components Overview</h2>
        <p>Blazor components are the fundamental building blocks of a Blazor application. Each component is a self-contained piece of UI with its own logic and styling.</p>
        
        <div class="code-block">
            <div class="code-header">CourseCard.razor - Basic Component Structure</div>
            <pre><code>@@* This is a Razor comment *@@

@@* HTML markup with Razor syntax *@@
&lt;div class="course-card"&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;@@Course.Title&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;@@Course.Description&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;span&gt;$@@Course.Price.ToString("F2")&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

@@code {
    // C# code block
    [Parameter]
    public CourseDto Course { get; set; } = null!;
    
    // Component logic goes here
}</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>ðŸ“¦ Component Anatomy:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Markup section:</strong> HTML with Razor syntax for dynamic content</li>
                <li><strong>@@code block:</strong> C# code for component logic</li>
                <li><strong>Parameters:</strong> Properties decorated with [Parameter] for passing data</li>
                <li><strong>CSS file:</strong> Optional isolated styles (ComponentName.razor.css)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="directives" class="tutorial-section">
        <h2>2. Blazor Directives</h2>
        <p>Directives are special instructions that tell Blazor how to handle components and elements.</p>
        
        <div class="directive-grid">
            <div class="directive-card">
                <h4>@@page</h4>
                <p>Defines a route for the component</p>
                <code>@@page "/courses"</code>
            </div>
            
            <div class="directive-card">
                <h4>@@inject</h4>
                <p>Injects a service via dependency injection</p>
                <code>@@inject CourseService Service</code>
            </div>
            
            <div class="directive-card">
                <h4>@@implements</h4>
                <p>Implements an interface</p>
                <code>@@implements IDisposable</code>
            </div>
            
            <div class="directive-card">
                <h4>@@inherits</h4>
                <p>Inherits from a base class</p>
                <code>@@inherits ComponentBase</code>
            </div>
            
            <div class="directive-card">
                <h4>@@rendermode</h4>
                <p>Sets the component's render mode</p>
                <code>@@rendermode InteractiveServer</code>
            </div>
            
            <div class="directive-card">
                <h4>@@attribute</h4>
                <p>Applies an attribute to the component</p>
                <code>@@attribute [Authorize]</code>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h3>Conditional Rendering</h3>
        <div class="code-block">
            <div class="code-header">Conditional & Loop Directives</div>
            <pre><code>@@* Conditional rendering *@@
